{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f8b2f11713cce1d54abeca31",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "给小鼠的房子",
        "text_hash": "e6f28f126f33b8d9b6327992cf972b779c1364cd7879e360b8871226718077fc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6b0763d4bc845c0e28412c58",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠看着远处的一座黄色房子。",
        "text_hash": "b5f4a4ae377b66f8f38a9729e625f58f3f757d80f262c96ea44f134c1ae852da",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c4bf1e54c768891bd4f1557c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠正在寻找一座新房子。",
        "text_hash": "322d50b57a2391fefff8c5bf20330f0b17607c05243be9a08859c9aafd2b0b4d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8d3adbd8584eb457ec9d6dc0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "前门半开着。小鼠往里面看。",
        "text_hash": "05e2ce704817f99bdade181e54b25dc3927ecc03980d35b162830440c8eeaedf",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_58f693f2bb4bed96d27d59bb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这看起来像是一座不错的房子。",
        "text_hash": "09a5ed1267d63ab6a742a6cbd44edccdb34fa263a4c257422392fa6755571be6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2990c655a179a0a25f1c8b8f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一只黑色小狗伸着长长的舌头，邀请小鼠加入他。",
        "text_hash": "baa62de1330bcda454ee1ea2a83fab5b56e970b2329fd64fe2ccc777934ebf98",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1518ba118b3c85232d2a249f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“你可以来和我一起睡，”小狗说。",
        "text_hash": "9d6c1cfb203479af408f11b835874ef08f2c5c17b6f4ae23db7bcb0e20dafc61",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_083075d704cf5c9c1e03533d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“谢谢你，”小鼠说。",
        "text_hash": "27c2914ff1c7d1c12983bccad239216326169b43b60bded1824c704017c67e5d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_010529eead3589c6ebc06ca0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠睡在一摊泥里。",
        "text_hash": "a2fbd660a59622f51697b801e228bce087cc351236fac965c39dda35f6864d77",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a0bfe873cb688968b4fdbe4d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "那天晚上，小鼠的梦又颠簸又泥泞。",
        "text_hash": "f48c1308014117e2bff8216831e8a388af683de087e9e82f476ed6f683b59bbb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f533fc03aa246782a7425571",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一只色彩鲜艳的鹦鹉站在栖木上，邀请小鼠加入他。",
        "text_hash": "30f80bf014ef337f0d644c85f91e2d5379bdaa786766512cef90a230ccad4579",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9615247e253cee85d12f86f8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“你可以来和我一起睡，”鹦鹉说。",
        "text_hash": "8d1a7b011903177e21331bb4af40b77520853d7a38fc0a1a718b4334d8e6c55d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a6605fe1145af2060649b560",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“谢谢你，”小鼠说。",
        "text_hash": "27c2914ff1c7d1c12983bccad239216326169b43b60bded1824c704017c67e5d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a32391e2133ffac6ae1e0e38",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠睡在一片狂野的森林里。",
        "text_hash": "dac348505bf9d77d3e5f216f6f00d16e2ad109e0f3d44b49ee7493aa8d75ed03",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b94622a8efb56bce29b10b9c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "那天晚上，小鼠的梦又吵闹又狂野。",
        "text_hash": "288ac89c3f071e9c1fba62401d64f895feeea270f64a7fabc72f12cf75a22461",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0a3726485bdde45754f3fcb8",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一条在鱼缸里游动的金鱼邀请小鼠加入他。",
        "text_hash": "5b24be5de0b5f8227b7e5f03bf07d041835a16d17188ec25abebab6157eab7ba",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a3414cca971f249d0fe1aec4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“你可以来和我一起睡，”鱼说。",
        "text_hash": "f76ae9957b8bc65729df2deffd8262cf2b163744b6b525047cd1fe5afb401ad8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9be8d60e25ec6621e3040c3f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "“谢谢你，”小鼠说。",
        "text_hash": "27c2914ff1c7d1c12983bccad239216326169b43b60bded1824c704017c67e5d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_63a06d56ef6de66d299fd40e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠睡在水下，周围是鱼和海草。",
        "text_hash": "44bcd30addcbadb9ce25136a7fcbd5b1c9fb7de07b5175c1cd1b687e4d1829e7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_49a6d87998427aa8ed0a8afc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "那天晚上，小鼠的梦又冷又湿。",
        "text_hash": "63455a6cd06322d6e8c9bb3d80efe0dc78b1294b09d6312dbce7655d7b4d1895",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_932beeb7d56300fa8bd19a2a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠飞快地从踢脚板旁跑过。",
        "text_hash": "1e01715e1ce84b35493d63afc1574703a7db1581d6ff35f47321beda700a2402",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d0d7eba5dc0f62306fa86437",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠需要一个温暖干燥的地方。",
        "text_hash": "a1178d2f3a4c8818f47ad8a2c93599363c96236c608779288fe785bb437643b2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_788349f4140d34841fc7a78e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠栖在壁炉前的一张沙发上。",
        "text_hash": "90fd8842d9dc4b34b3bd6ab8f4265915c2b77d83717ef271f6d6ee6c557ee223",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_95e7ecc2ade5bf5d0c474269",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "一个漂亮的书架。",
        "text_hash": "8b7dc329544b97f81689e298a069c11f6d61be5dbe62d6885359a275c8ab5e76",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_956a1670afd10da4d5ddb1fa",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠在附近找到了一个书架。",
        "text_hash": "1728ee551db48a730304ffc6ef02f5cbe39f4d578094351731ffe3928eaa30c9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bc8f0a7f813539ec03a9a4c5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小鼠安静地睡着了。",
        "text_hash": "a7dbab71b3a77363df50182642d4449d2513e0116c17635f1d3bcbf50a6cee5e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7b5bc4a997d9b82841f25030",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "那天晚上，小鼠做了温暖又舒适的梦。",
        "text_hash": "61cc33e9d1f305dbc9c25d893f85f5945b969188836a65d8ddcd9f13a1ed06da",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_c3d8d69cdc5656942c52f9d9"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
